到好多細舖仔，<br />\n但唔係營業廳黎，<br />\n一張55蚊卡賣100蚊同200蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你揾中移動都冇用，一樣上唔到google .<br />\n要上到google同fb youtube個張卡必需在香港買"},{"pid":"bed0dcc5d1cb2ab7d703439d702eee19729f55ef","tid":331470,"uid":127876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人知羅湖中國移動營業廳係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngoogle過地址係羅湖交通層5號舖，<br />\n但係問啲保安都唔知交通層係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家係大陸又用唔到google，<br />\n可唔可以救救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出左羅湖關，直行去地鐵站，行一陣見到有</blockquote><br />\n我行到尾見到好似有個閘口，<br />\n跟住前面好似無咩舖，<br />\n我就上咗一層又有好多閘口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係我唔知邊度係地鐵站，<br />\n我一出關就不停向前行，<br />\n係咪行錯咗路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你出關冇上一層<br />\n就應該去到地鐵站<br />\n我記得有間中移動？？</blockquote><br />\n我&hellip;&hellip;路痴&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n唔知有冇上一層&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n我見到好多細舖仔，<br />\n但唔係營業廳黎，<br />\n一張55蚊卡賣100蚊同200蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你揾中移動都冇用，一樣上唔到google .<br />\n要上到google同fb youtube個張卡必需在香港買</blockquote><br />\n我知呀，我唔駛上google,fb,youtube個啲，<br />\n因為我通常係上去半日，<br />\n所以先想買日租卡，起碼叫whatsapp有得上吓線，<br />\n唔會失聯咁。"},{"pid":"9a46c6009ffe949876a0e676d77e617f83d30b5a","tid":331470,"uid":7956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"但我上星期上華強<br />\n不論聯通移動電信都話無日租卡比香港人<br />\n得d 月費plan<br />\n係未佢水鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e759b8601b3eba01ee9a216a4605c84b0a08e984","